  <TR><TD ALIGN="left" WIDTH="150">Looking through the form of the<BR ALIGN='left'/>transaction of January 1, 1939, and<BR ALIGN='left'/>getting into the substance, it appears<BR ALIGN='left'/>to me plainly that it was a merger or<BR ALIGN='left'/>consolidation and nothing more.</TD></TR>
