  <TR><TD ALIGN="left" WIDTH="150">&quot;(1) that the transferor corporation or<BR ALIGN='left'/>its shareholders retained a substantial<BR ALIGN='left'/>proprietary stake in the enterprise<BR ALIGN='left'/>represented by a material interest in<BR ALIGN='left'/>the affairs of the transferee<BR ALIGN='left'/>corporation, and, (2) that such retained<BR ALIGN='left'/>interest represents a substantial part<BR ALIGN='left'/>of the value of the property<BR ALIGN='left'/>transferred.&quot;</TD></TR>
